{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Improbability Control Bureau&quot; is a spot-the-difference horror game. Monitor live surveillance cameras. Spot anomalies. From eerie furniture shifts to unexpected intrusions, report anomalies to correct them and survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As an agent of a classified organization, your mission is to monitor the live surveillance camera footage of locations reaching dangerously high levels of improbability and restore them to normality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Note: There is only one level (with two slight variants) </i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Shine your spotlight to report and disable anomalies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530060/extras/reporting-gif-3.gif?t=1733782457\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survive the night and before all normality is lost forever!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2026 Was that always there? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle a growing sense of paranoia, armed only with your sharp eyes and memory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530060/extras/reporting-gif-1.gif?t=1733782457\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Improbability Control Bureau awaits! Are you prepared to safeguard normality in the face of improbability?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>This game was made by a 2 person team: my girlfriend and I. She is responsible for most of the level design and overall art direction. While I have been primarily focused on developing the Improbability Engine that supports it. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Thank you for your continued support! </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_par